rComments: WIsh I dropped her class. Talked so fast the first half of the year she could have been a rapper signed by Lil Wayne. So due to this no one in class got complete lecture notes from the first half of the year until exams. By then it was to late, comprehension was down the drain.

Looking at the reviews from 7~8 years ago, it seems that she has improved drastically in her teaching skills. Very helpful- great communication skills with students. Her pharmacy and sociology combination is great!

Excellent teacher. Incredibly intelligent and slightly intimidating. My mentor! Only enjoyable, however, if you are a student who loves to learn and do they work. If your looking for an easy credit, you will be disappointed.
